## âœ… Final Step: Add `.gitattributes` (Important)

To make sure GitHub shows Dart as the **main language**, create a file in the **root** of your project named `.gitattributes` and add:

```gitattributes
*.dart linguist-language=Dart
*.md linguist-documentation
*.yaml linguist-documentation
*.yml linguist-documentation
*.json linguist-documentation
assets/** linguist-vendored
